# Anki-workflow core

Read `AGENTS.md` and `workflow_status.md` before bulk work.

- Cards from `lectures/**/processed/**` and `lectures/**/cards/` only — not `raw/` PDFs
- Extract new PDFs with `batch_extract_course.py` before creating cards
- Backup in `backups/` before Anki imports >5 cards
- Permanent scripts in `scripts/`; ephemeral helpers in `scripts/_scratch/`
- Update `workflow_status.md` after extraction, import, or backup
